entries.femaleVariant: Say, by the way... What do you know about biochips? Arasaka's "Relic," in particular.
Well, it's designed to store a person's neural engram. Er, sorry... just imagine copying over a person's memories and personality.
What do you know about Arasaka's "Relic?"
Right, I get that. More curious what happens if the stored engram overwrites the engrams of the chip carrier.
"Overwrites?" I... I'm not even sure that's possible...
Nah, never mind... Not a big deal. Thanks.
